repository.name: CoffeeWithCloudySpartans
repository.description: Developed an Online Coffee Store application using Mongo, Express, React, Node (MERN) and Go. Hosted the data service API modules developed in Go as microservices using Kubernetes. Aim is to demonstrate right use the cloud technologies following industry standards in terms of security, scalability and efficiency.
